name: UAutomatedAssetImportData
doc: Contains data for a group of assets to import

GroupName: Display name of the group. This is for logging purposes only.
DestinationPath: Content path in the projects content directory where assets will be imported
FactoryName: Name of the factory to use when importing these assets. If not specified the factory type will be auto detected
bReplaceExisting: Whether or not to replace existing assets
bSkipReadOnly: Whether or not to skip importing over read only assets that could not be checked out
Factory: Pointer to the factory currently being used
LevelToLoad: Full path to level to load before importing this group (only matters if importing assets into a level)
